{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0afc3d3da1","title":"谢富治谈谭震林问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a524b05ce2","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"0afc3d3da1"}],"tags":[{"id":"89f0012853","name":"谭震林","type":"人物"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"85b13f5c0b","name":"谢富治"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bc3ec9f33f","type":"title","text":"谢富治谈谭震林问题","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"0d5bc5fdc3","type":"authors","text":"谢富治","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"1b55a521cd","type":"appellation","text":"〖1967年5月14日下午两点，在市革委会全体委员会议前就农林口问题请示了谢副总理〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"9105aafb2b","type":"paragraph","text":"问：现在外面传说，毛主席在一次会上说过：有人不是要打倒谭震林？他今天还参加会来了！毛主席真这样说过吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"0cb559654a","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：没有这么回事，我参加会议没有听见主席这么说过，这是有人造谣！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"72e397de3f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：今后农林口的问题怎么搞？谭震林的问题怎么搞？","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"ffbf57b2fd","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：你们自己干嘛！继续深入地批判他！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"a7907154f4","type":"paragraph","text":"说：谭震林五月一日上天安门后，农林口形势有很大变化，他的秘书吕伊波五月二日突然死去了，有恐怖气氛！","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"4e68506d57","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：吕伊波揭发了谭震林吗？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"ae7424423f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：他写了一个揭发谭震林问题的提纲，还来不及揭发，就突然死去了，死的原因我们正在调查。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"},{"id":"d330c6b21c","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：不论过去、现在，或者将来，你们批判谭震林的错误都是对的。即使将来给他工作，你们批判他也是对的。保守派要保就是错的。你们可以把这些问题反映给总理。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1"}],"page":{"id":"a9f708db78","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"0afc3d3da1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}